summary: I am a foreign Medical Doctor graduate with a vast experience in clinical care African's area such as normal consultations and emergencies of pediatrics departement and adults by: participating in multidisciplinary clinical care teams; taking care of adults patients, babies and children; supporting health services research on outcomes of care; providing patient education; writing report; and furthering public health initiatives such as diabetes and hypertensives education, prevention program against sexually transmitted diseases. My experience has also expanded to include in recent years area of clinical research with knouwledge in data analysis on R and SPSS. As a highly motivated, reliable, confident, and a great team player dedicated to my profession, I am seeking to join a potential company that will challenge me to bring along not only my enthusiasm and my excellent communication skills in French, English and Dutch, but above all, my experiences in all domains pertaining to the clinical resarch field.
